[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "simple-agent"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "simple-agent"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"
publish = false

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.98"
handlebars = "6.3.2"
reqwest = "0.12.18"
serde_json = "1.0.140"
serde_yml = "0.0.12"
tracing = "0.1.41"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.39"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.ollama-rs]
version = "0.2.2"
features = ["chat-history"]

[dependencies.openai-api-rs]
version = "6.0.6"
features = ["rustls"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.219"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.45.1"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread", "fs", "process", "signal"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.19"
features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.17.0"
features = ["v4"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "simple_agent"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]
